---------------------------------------------------------------------------
Third-party components
---------------------------------------------------------------------------

Verdigris embeds and builds upon the following open-source projects. Each is
distributed under its own license; this NOTICE is informational only.

  - Apache Arrow / Apache Parquet (Apache-2.0) — columnar in-memory format and
    the on-disk file format logs are written to.
  - Apache DataFusion (Apache-2.0) — the SQL query engine that reads Parquet
    directly from object storage.
  - object_store (Apache-2.0 / MIT) — the storage abstraction over S3, local
    filesystem, and in-memory backends.
  - tokio, axum, tower-http (MIT) — the async runtime and HTTP server.
  - madsim (Apache-2.0) — the deterministic simulator used for testing.

A complete, machine-readable inventory of dependencies and their licenses is
available from the Cargo manifests (`Cargo.toml`, `Cargo.lock`); run
`cargo tree` or `cargo about` to generate it.
